{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/wl.gif?t=1729538238\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/demodivider.png?t=1729538238\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/dog.gif?t=1729538238\" /><br>Detective Dotson distills the Indian experience into an adventure mystery game.<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br>\ud83d\udd7aBollywood dancing.<br>\ud83d\ude98Crazy traffic.<br>\ud83e\uded6High tea with nosy aunties.<br>And of course\u2026<br>\ud83d\udc36 You can pet the dog.<br><br>\ud83d\udd0dFind clues and complete an evidence board to solve each case.<br>\ud83c\udfadEngage with an array of characters as vibrant as India itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/demodivider.png?t=1729538238\" /><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/wedding.gif?t=1729538238\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/demodivider.png?t=1729538238\" /><br>The FOMO-mergency\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br>This demo gives you a quick but spicy taste of Detective Dotson in the Mystery of Mrs. Sengupta\u2019s FOMO-mergency. Explore freely, try out disguises and solve a case for your dear nosy aunty. <br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br>You see, she has been banned from high tea. You must infiltrate this esteemed party and get all the deets.<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br>And if the aunties are too mean to you, you can collect flowers for a cute grandma, help the police catch litterers by throwing garbage at them, and find kites for a school kid, among other activities.<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/flower.gif?t=1729538238\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/India.png?t=1729538238\" /><br>Between the colorful temple alleys and cozy apartment complexes lies the most wholesome place ever - home. Come have an adventure in the place we call home and give us your feedback so we can improve the full game!<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/temple.gif?t=1729538238\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2577650?t=1729538238","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1729538238","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729538238","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729538238","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/wl.gif?t=1729538238\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577650/extras/demodivider.png?